    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Institutions owning or maintaining collections of photographs, sometimes including other visual resources in various formats and media, usually within larger libraries, archives, or collections.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047354/Harrod's Librarians' Glossary (2000)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Instellingen, gewoonlijk deel uitmakend van grotere bibliotheken, archieven of collecties, die collecties van foto's en soms ander visueel materiaal in verschillende vormen en op verschillende media in bezit hebben of onderhouden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>擁有或負責保管維護照片的機構，其館藏有時亦包含以其他形式或媒材呈現之視覺資源，通常附設於規模較大的圖書館、資料館或典藏機構之下。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
